      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i've had asthma for a long time but lately i feel like i'm getting out of breath just walking a few steps to the kitchen or even just sitting up. i'm getting older so maybe my lungs are just not what they used to be? or should i just take an extra puff of my ventolin if i feel it coming on?",
