    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just a bit scary to think it's that serious. i've been feeling a bit lightheaded too when i get winded, and some of my chest feels tight, but i dont want to go to the hospital for something that might just be aging or stress. is there something i can take at home to settle my breathing so i dont have to bother a doctor?",
